{"tid":1359318,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（遍地開花）一位熱愛香港既醫療輔助隊隊員","createTime":"2019-07-24T06:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T19:53:35.000Z","uid":272719,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e35b2e6cf76ff41d44a9027abf95ca07e4b5836d","tid":1359318,"uid":272719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:12:47.000Z","msg":"致各位香港市民<br />\n<br />\n成為首屈一指的志願應急醫療衛生組織。藉着一支訓練有素、專業和全情投入的志願隊伍，以最高效率和最具成效的方式，提供資源來增強常規醫療衛生服務，使香港市民得享健康安全的生活。<br />\n<br />\n我係一位熱愛香港既普通市民，加入醫療輔助隊係希望可以幫助每一位市民，喺危急關頭拯救生命<br />\n<br />\n由6月9號至到而家每一次嘅光復行動我都有出席，但最令我深刻嘅事7月21號元朗官警黑合作，當日我喺天水圍警署請求警察出動去元朗拯救市民，但係驚你嘅答覆係警署竟然拉閘，係呢個無助既時刻，我不禁流下一滴男兒淚，我喊嘅原因係因為警察件係呢個危急嘅時候竟然選擇唔拯救市民嘅生命，反而同黑社會同流合污，對付一般嘅市民。 <br />\n<br />\n所以我希望可以喺度追究警察濫權，成立獨立調查委員會，並反對元朗721嘅警黑合作，並要求政府全面撤回送中條例。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TPABRTS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTPABRTS.png&h=731a26aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6f2e2b9d11ce0de294c5fc45f6820eb2f60645f","tid":1359318,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:17:27.000Z","msg":"元朗手足有野講 727去唔去都入黎睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ab49938b797e929e5ca5850ca4dcd8da4fdf8b4d","tid":1359318,"uid":236404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:24:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"96ba40058ef7e097a660cfdc96f0527763b2eb00","tid":1359318,"uid":263464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WBojPN7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWBojPN7.gif&h=6b8a4951&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8caafc7e9a06de460be49875022c066dce6b6e7e","tid":1359318,"uid":24466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:36:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adfc8bd0618aa73e0f2bf87babbb0ce319e4030","tid":1359318,"uid":138296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:39:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28e7c0cb42469661748e7b09cd6d186a4f6f877b","tid":1359318,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:47:55.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"45491e3480c4ad1c0b25bde223aac04f4ce74846","tid":1359318,"uid":267189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:51:18.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲<br />\n小弟見到好多遍地開花嘅post，好感動<br />\n不同行業嘅巴絲都出嚟發聲<br />\n<br />\n但係因為連登啲post好散同埋facebook接觸到嘅年齡層面相對連登會更加廣<br />\n所以開一個facebook page去整合一啲政府部門同公營機構嘅遍地開花post裡面嘅相<br />\n<br />\n點解淨係整政府部門同公營機構呢？<br />\n因為佢哋發聲嘅震撼力比較大同埋小弟能力有限，未能夠整合晒各行各業嘅post<br />\n<br />\n如果有巴絲其實只係想post喺連登，而唔想擺喺facebook，歡迎pm我，我會即刻delete返<br />\n<br />\n而如果有喺政府部門或者公營機構工作嘅巴絲想post去facebook，歡迎喺facebook pm呢個page: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/civilservantsflowers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcivilservantsflowers&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe0qdoMPUcUEfVTbHbk%2Bo2EU%3D&h=f443757d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/civilservantsflowers</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做"},{"pid":"ba44814446efe86131281514389ddb466466bbb5","tid":1359318,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:53:35.000Z","msg":"多謝你呀"}]}